#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:106
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Protocols and Ports` page, make sure :guilabel:`TCP` "
"and :guilabel:`Specified local ports` are selected, enter the following in "
"the field: `8069, 80, 443`, and click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page :guilabel:`Protocols and Ports`, s'assurer que :guilabel:`TCP` "
"et :guilabel:`Specified local ports` sont sélectionnés, saisir ce qui suit "
"dans le champ : `8069, 80, 443`, et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:111
msgid ""
"Other ports may be necessary depending on your IoT devices. For example, for "
"the :doc:`/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/"
"worldline` payment terminal, add the `9050` port."
msgstr ""
"D'autres ports peuvent être nécessaires selon les périphériques IoT. Par "
"exemple, pour le terminal de paiement :doc:`/applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/worldline`, ajouter le port `9050`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:115
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Action` page, select :guilabel:`Allow the connection` and "
"click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page :guilabel:`Action`, sélectionner :guilabel:`Allow the "
"connection` et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:117
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Profile` page, disable any connection type(s) that don't "
"apply to your Windows computer and click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page :guilabel:`Profile`, désactiver tout type de connexion qui ne "
"s'applique pas à votre ordinateur Windows et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:119
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Name` page, provide a :guilabel:`Name` (e.g., `Odoo`) and, "
"optionally, a brief :guilabel:`Description`, then click :guilabel:`Finish`."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page :guilabel:`Name`, fournir un :guilabel:`Name` (par exemple, "
"`Odoo`) et, éventuellement, une brève :guilabel:`Description`, puis cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Finish`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:123
msgid ""
"`Windows Firewall rules documentation <https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/"
